{"id":479,"date":"2020-02-14T23:00:27","date_gmt":"2020-02-14T16:00:27","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=479"},"modified":"2021-08-22T08:22:08","modified_gmt":"2021-08-22T01:22:08","slug":"thoai-mai-lua-tai-lieu-ngu-van-lop-12-o-bai-viet-nay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/02\/14\/thoai-mai-lua-tai-lieu-ngu-van-lop-12-o-bai-viet-nay\/","title":{"rendered":"Tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i l\u1ef1a t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u Ng\u1eef V\u0103n l\u1edbp 12 \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft v\u0103n hay, theo m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch, b\u00e1o th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ecdc c\u00e1c ti\u1ec3u thuy\u1ebft kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1t, l\u1ed1i suy ngh\u0129. \u0110\u1ecdc b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 &#8211; v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin di\u1ec5n ra h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m nh\u1eadn vi\u1ebft v\u0103n hay, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ed5n so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a d\u00e2n kh\u1ed1i A. M\u00ecnh hay \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch ti\u1ec3u thuy\u1ebft kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. V\u00e0 th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n &#8220;Ru\u1ed3i tr\u00e2u&#8221;. Sau cu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y, m\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00f2ng nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a thanh ni\u00ean. C\u00f2n b\u00e1o th\u00ec m\u00ecnh hay \u0111\u1ecdc onl \u1edf c\u00e1c trang nh\u01b0 D\u00e2n tr\u00ed (c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, kinh t\u1ebf), newszing (c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a, \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i), v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Kenh14 (trang n\u00e0y h\u01a1i x\u00e0m t\u00ed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh th\u1ed1ng cho l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb, showbiz,&#8230;). M\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 m\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n kh\u1ed1i C c\u0169ng n\u00ean t\u00ecm m\u1ea5y trang b\u00e1o theo s\u1edf th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u00e9. V\u1eeba h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i vi\u1ebft, v\u1eeba bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i &#8211; bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u sau n\u00e0y tr\u00fang t\u1ee7 c\u00e2u ngh\u1ecb lu\u1eadn x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec sao. \u0110\u00fang kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng sau \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u hay ho. \u0110\u1ee7 c\u00e1c th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb s\u00e1ch, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01b0\u01a1ng,&#8230; M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o ch\u1ecdn ra c\u00e1i m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i t\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc nh\u00e9. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong file n\u00e0y c\u00f3 2 cu\u1ed1n &#8220;C\u1eedu \u00e2m ch\u00e2n kinh&#8221; v\u00e0 &#8220;Ng\u1ecdc n\u1eef t\u00e2m kinh&#8221; c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Nh\u1eadt T\u0169n kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 hay ho. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1 thi n\u1eefa. N\u00f3i chung l\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Kh\u1ecfi lo kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i \u01b0ng \u00fd. Ch\u00fac m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nha!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9: <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=1pOE4ze9icceMntxn4LUDcoP9uIbiZ4uF\">https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=1pOE4ze9icceMntxn4LUDcoP9uIbiZ4uF<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>\u0110\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft v\u0103n hay, theo m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec? Theo m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch, b\u00e1o th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ecdc c\u00e1c ti\u1ec3u thuy\u1ebft kinh <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/02\/14\/thoai-mai-lua-tai-lieu-ngu-van-lop-12-o-bai-viet-nay\/\" title=\"Tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i l\u1ef1a t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u Ng\u1eef V\u0103n l\u1edbp 12 \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y!\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":480,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[13,7,4],"tags":[83,195,209,21,208],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/479"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=479"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/479\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":481,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/479\/revisions\/481"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/480"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=479"}],"wp:term"